description: Italian dining emporium with groceries, seafood markets & a dozen eateries.
Butcher shop & grocery store specializing in high-end meats, cheeses, bread & produce since 1939.
Gourmet groceries & imported specialty foods, plus sandwiches, a salad bar & hot dishes to go.
Grocery store & deli counter, popular with the college set for late-night snacks & subs.
We strive to be your go-to neighborhood supermarket, providing our customers and partners with a central point of service, value and experience.

We provide fresh fruits and vegetables, prepared take-away and specialty items, meats and deli, dairy, coffee, baked goods, and household supplies so you can pop in and out to get exactly what you need.
We strive to be your go-to neighborhood supermarket, providing our customers and partners with a central point of service, value and experience.

We are a family owned grocery store. Our purpose is to provide the community with healthy food
choices. We have a variety in grocery, produce, meat, deli, dairy, frozen, takeout (coming soon).
